                    <p>The foregoing is a listing of significant unshipped items. Miscellaneous
                        other items requested by the Chinese Government remain to be procured and/or
                        shipped. A rough estimate of the dollar value of all unshipped items, by
                        federal agencies concerned, is as follows: <table cols="2"
                            rendition="#center-block" rows="5">
