                            </row>
                        </table>
                    </p>
                    <p>The following list covers military materiel being procured by the Chinese
                        through commercial sources in this country on which as yet unused export
                        licenses have been issued. Some of the items listed are being procured with
                        funds from the $125 Million Grants, but the exact quantity of such items is
                        not known.</p>
                    <pb facs="0606" n="596" xml:id="pg_596"/>
                    <p rend="flushleft">A. <hi rend="italic">Items other than Aircraft and Aircraft
